sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/Dashboard
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Controller as ODH Model Controller<br/>Leader-Elected Pod
    participant SMMR as Service Mesh<br/>Member Roll
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus Operator
    participant Router as OpenShift Router
    participant Storage as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over User,Storage: Flow 1: InferenceService Creation (KServe Serverless)

    User->>K8sAPI: Create InferenceService CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: Watch Event<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS Edge TLS
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Add Namespace to SMMR<br/>Enable Istio Sidecar
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create PeerAuthentication<br/>mTLS: PERMISSIVE
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Telemetry<br/>Metrics Config
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create ServiceMonitor<br/>Port: 8080/TCP
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create PodMonitor<br/>Istio Metrics: 15020/TCP
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create NetworkPolicy<br/>Ingress/Egress Rules
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create metrics Service<br/>{isvc-name}-metrics

    K8sAPI-->>User: InferenceService Ready

    Note over User,Storage: Flow 2: Storage Secret Aggregation

    User->>K8sAPI: Create Data Connection Secret<br/>S3 Credentials
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: Watch Secret Event<br/>Label: opendatahub.io/managed=true

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Read All Data Connection Secrets<br/>In Namespace
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create/Update storage-config Secret<br/>Aggregated Credentials

    Note over Controller,Storage: KServe/ModelMesh uses storage-config
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Read storage-config
    K8sAPI-->>Storage: Download Model Artifacts<br/>Auth: AWS Credentials

    Note over User,Storage: Flow 3: Monitoring Access Provisioning

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create RoleBinding<br/>prometheus-ns-access
    K8sAPI-->>Prometheus: Grant Access to Namespace

    Prometheus->>K8sAPI: Discover ServiceMonitor
    Prometheus->>K8sAPI: Scrape InferenceService Pod<br/>8080/TCP HTTP<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    Prometheus->>K8sAPI: Scrape Istio Proxy<br/>15020/TCP HTTP<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
